Cell["\<\
Reference 6 develops the differential-geometry background, from a physicist\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s perspective, necessary for the theoretical developments \
in References 1, 2, 3, and 9. That\[CloseCurlyQuote]s all we have to say \
about theory in this notebook.\
\>", "Item",
