   SubscriptBox["I", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0e7947ab-8ad0-4ecd-a039-d6e35a9c9cad"],
 " are constants. Rewrite their total time derivatives to zero (it\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s interesting in some problems to let them vary with time, \
